This result is obtained from the following SPARQL query to Wikidata:

```sparql
SELECT ?elementLabel WHERE {
  ?element wdt:P31 wd:Q11344;     # Instance of chemical element
           wdt:P575 ?date .        # Time of discovery
  SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en". }
}
ORDER BY DESC(?date)
LIMIT 5
```
